Easy 5-min appetizer using @crunchmastercrackers to satisfy that crunch 💛 Crunchmaster = guilt-free enjoyment with great taste, trustworthy ingredients, and feel-good nutrition.☀️ Purchase them at your local Public in the deli section. 

INGREDIENTS
	•	6 slices bacon, cooked & crumbled
	•	11 oz goat cheese, softened
	•	Hot honey, for drizzling
	•	Fresh cracked black pepper
	•	Crunchmaster crackers

DIRECTIONS
Whip goat cheese in a food processor until smooth. Spread on a plate, drizzle with hot honey, and top with bacon, green onions, and black pepper. Serve with Crunchmaster crackers!
